over three tons
of cement dust.

00:43:53.665 --> 00:43:55.932
Half the guys
still haven't
recovered.

00:43:56.068 --> 00:43:57.470
(ALL GRUNT ANGRILY)

00:43:57.606 --> 00:44:00.502
