00:44:20.896 --> 00:44:22.329
Uh...
EMBER: No.

00:44:22.465 --> 00:44:23.926
Right?

00:44:24.061 --> 00:44:26.496
(EMBER CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY)
Right! I am not
an inspector.

00:44:27.437 --> 00:44:28.833
(BUBBLING)

00:44:28.968 --> 00:44:30.231
You are inspector.

00:44:30.366 --> 00:44:31.642
Why you poking around?

00:44:31.777 --> 00:44:33.172
Is this because
of water leak?

00:44:33.307 --> 00:44:36.343
No. Not because
of water in any way.

00:44:36.478 --> 00:44:39.017
(CHUCKLES)
He's a different
kind of inspector.

00:44:39.152 --> 00:44:40.075
Right?

00:44:40.211 --> 00:44:41.945
Yeah. Yeah. I'm a...

00:44:42.080 --> 00:44:44.846
I'm a food inspector.

00:44:44.982 --> 00:44:47.449
