Hmm. I think
he's lying through his feet.

00:44:50.562 --> 00:44:52.120
Teeth.
Whatever.

00:44:52.256 --> 00:44:53.726
Food upstairs. Come.

00:44:53.861 --> 00:44:55.198
Food inspector?

00:44:55.334 --> 00:44:56.257
I panicked.

00:44:56.393 --> 00:44:57.835
(GROANS IN FRUSTRATION)

00:44:59.000 --> 00:45:00.602
You really
food inspector?

00:45:00.738 --> 00:45:02.334
As far as you know, yeah.

00:45:03.409 --> 00:45:06.106
Then inspect this.

00:45:06.241 --> 00:45:07.410
Dad.
(SPEAKING FIRISH) E shutsh!

00:45:07.546 --> 00:45:09.338
(AMUSING MUSIC PLAYING)

00:45:09.474 --> 00:45:10.875
(SNIFFS) Yep, all looks
good to me.

00:45:11.011 --> 00:45:12.110
No, no, no,
no, no.

00:45:12.245 --> 00:45:15.044
Inspect with
your mouth.

