(MUNCHES, BLOWS)

00:45:18.216 --> 00:45:19.450
(CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY)

00:45:20.789 --> 00:45:22.992
(BLOWS, CHUCKLES)

00:45:24.431 --> 00:45:25.889
(CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY)

00:45:26.024 --> 00:45:27.722
(WHIMPERS)

00:45:30.269 --> 00:45:31.233
Ah.

00:45:31.369 --> 00:45:32.465
(FIZZES)

00:45:32.601 --> 00:45:33.596
(GULPS)

00:45:34.934 --> 00:45:36.737
(STIFLED GROAN)

00:45:36.872 --> 00:45:38.268
(FOOD THUDS)
(SCREAMS)

00:45:38.403 --> 00:45:40.277
(MUFFLED SCREAM)
(BUBBLING)

00:45:40.412 --> 00:45:41.637
(MUFFLED GRUNT)

00:45:42.711 --> 00:45:44.513
(SCREAMS)

00:45:44.649 --> 00:45:47.342
You see?
He likes it.

00:45:47.477 --> 00:45:49.183
(COUGHING)
(CHUCKLES)

