You must try these.
Straight from Fire Land.

00:45:52.053 --> 00:45:53.517
Dad, those are too hot.

00:45:53.652 --> 00:45:55.655
(VOICE STRAINS)
I'm okay. I love hot food.

00:45:55.790 --> 00:45:57.125
(INHALES) Um.

