Actually,
after the heat
dies down,

00:46:12.545 --> 00:46:14.010
that's really good.

00:46:14.810 --> 00:46:16.144
If you don't mind.

00:46:18.274 --> 00:46:19.206
(SIZZLES)

00:46:19.342 --> 00:46:20.445
(GASPS) Mm-mm!

