00:46:40.067 --> 00:46:41.266
(EXCLAIMS IN FIRISH)

00:46:41.402 --> 00:46:43.099
Dad, don't worry.
I've got this.

00:46:43.234 --> 00:46:44.939
(SPEAKING FIRISH)

00:46:45.074 --> 00:46:46.544
Look, meet me
at the beach

00:46:46.679 --> 00:46:47.902
