say that?

00:48:17.669 --> 00:48:19.130
I'm a bad daughter.

00:48:19.265 --> 00:48:20.770
Hey, no.
(SOBS)

00:48:20.906 --> 00:48:22.297
You're doing
your best.

00:48:22.432 --> 00:48:24.298
(SNIFFLES, SIGHS)

00:48:24.433 --> 00:48:25.977
I'm a mess.

00:48:26.112 --> 00:48:28.771
