you're even more beautiful.

00:48:29.705 --> 00:48:31.675
(SENTIMENTAL MUSIC PLAYING)

00:48:40.686 --> 00:48:41.893
Maybe you're right
when you said

00:48:42.028 --> 00:48:44.757
my temper is me trying
to tell me something.

00:48:44.892 --> 00:48:45.955
(SIZZLES)

00:48:46.091 --> 00:48:47.592
Whoa.

00:48:47.728 --> 00:48:50.034
Look what
your fire did
to the sand.

00:48:50.935 --> 00:48:52.597
